title: PlayStation Joins Summer Game Fest! - Kinda Funny Games Daily 05.31.22
description:
Janet and Gary join each other FOR THE FIRST TIME on Games Daily to talk about PlayStation's Summer Games Fest, Pokemon, and the end of it all!

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:05:30 - Housekeeping

Every Kinda Funny Wrestling championship is on the line TODAY! Yes, KFW Memorial Day Brawl pops off after this episode of Kinda Funny Games Daily. Come see if Joey Noelle can knock off Alanah Pearce and become the Kinda Funny Twitch Champion! If you miss it live, it’ll be up ASAP on youtube.com/kindafunnygames.

The Roper Report  -
